"(define (*<-proc lst)
  (let ([res (make-circuit #:external-pins (left right))])
    (for ([item lst])
      (hook-proc! res
                  (Net (list (pin-ref res 'left)
                             (pin-ref item 'left)))
                  (Net (list (pin-ref res 'right)
                             (pin-ref item 'right)))))
    res))"
